OL,5, Recent cases involving serious sexual  
OL,6, offences have taken the longest time on
OL,7, record to go through Crown Courts in   
OL,8, England and Wales, the BBC has found.  
OL,10,FExclusive data compiled by the BBC     
OL,11,Ffound such cases took an average of    
OL,12,Fnine months to complete in 2021, with  
OL,13,Fhuge variations between regions.       
OL,15,FCriminal barristers say the delays are 
OL,16,Fdue to funding cuts and a decision to  
OL,17,Freduce how many days judges could sit. 
OL,19,FBut Justice Secretary Dominic Raab said
OL,20,Fthey were caused by the pandemic.      
